OL,3,CChild in induced coma as drink and
OL,4,Cdrug driver crashes
OL,6,FA child was put in an induced coma and
OL,7,Fa pregnant woman suffered 'multiple
OL,8,Finjuries' after a crash involving a
OL,9,Fdrink and drug driver.
OL,11,FBirdie Trotter is in prison following
OL,12,Fthe incident on Warrington's Birchwood
OL,13,FWay ` which left the defendant
OL,14,F'medically trapped'.
OL,16,FThe 36-year-old had been driving with
OL,17,Ftwo young children in her car, while
OL,18,Fshe was over the limit for both drink
OL,19,Fand drugs.
