OL,3,CChild in induced coma as drink and
OL,4,Cdrug driver crashes
OL,6,FThe second child suffered bruising,
OL,7,Fwhile Trotter was medically trapped
OL,8,Finside the vehicle and sustained a
OL,9,Ffracture to her leg.
OL,11,FMeanwhile the Skoda driver, who was
OL,12,Fpregnant, and a passenger in the
OL,13,Fvehicle, suffered multiple injuries
OL,14,Fincluding cuts and bruises.
OL,16,FFollowing the incident, Trotter was
OL,17,Ftransported to hospital where tests
OL,18,Fwere conducted. She gave a reading of
OL,19,F137 milligrams of alcohol per 100
OL,20,Fmillilitres of blood.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
