OL,3,CChild in induced coma as drink and
OL,4,Cdrug driver crashes
OL,6,FThis exceeds the legal limit of 80
OL,7,Fmilligrams. She was also found to have
OL,8,F195 micrograms of Benzoylecgonine
OL,9,F(cocaine) per litre of blood, well
OL,10,Fover the limit of 50 micrograms.
OL,12,FTrotter, of Scott Street, Fairfield
OL,13,Fand Howley, Warrington, went on to
OL,14,Fadmit causing serious injury by
OL,15,Fdangerous driving, and drink driving
OL,16,Fand drug driving.
OL,18,FDuring a hearing at Liverpool Crown
OL,19,FCourt she was handed a 27-month jail
OL,20,Fterm.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
