OL,3,CChild in induced coma as drink and
OL,4,Cdrug driver crashes
OL,6,FIn addition she was banned from
OL,7,Fdriving for four years. Police have
OL,8,Fbacked the prison term.
OL,10,FPC Jamie Roberts said: "I welcome the
OL,11,Fcustodial sentence handed to Totter.
OL,12,FShe decided to not only get behind the
OL,13,Fwheel of a vehicle after drinking
OL,14,Falcohol and taking drugs, but also
OL,15,Fwith two young children in the car.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
