OL,6,F"She clearly showed no regard for the
OL,7,Fsafety of those children or the safety
OL,8,Fof other road users. Her dangerous
OL,9,Fdriving caused a number of injuries to
OL,10,Finnocent people, most seriously to a
OL,11,Fchild who spent days in an induced
OL,12,Fcoma as a result.
OL,14,F"The rules of the road are in place
OL,15,Ffor a reason and I hope Trotter spends
OL,16,Fher time in custody reflecting on her
OL,17,Fdecisions."
